423
00:28:51,646 --> 00:28:52,676
Are you insane?

424
00:28:55,485 --> 00:28:57,784
You know it's almost impossible...

425
00:28:57,785 --> 00:28:59,985
to prove you helped her escape.

426
00:29:00,755 --> 00:29:03,156
Why did you confess to that?

427
00:29:03,755 --> 00:29:06,055
Tell me. Your illness.

428
00:29:06,596 --> 00:29:07,666
It got bad, didn't it?

429
00:29:08,196 --> 00:29:10,065
That's the only explanation.

430
00:29:10,396 --> 00:29:12,906
So will he charge me for aiding and abetting?

431
00:29:13,836 --> 00:29:15,365
It'll be stay of prosecution.

432
00:29:15,366 --> 00:29:16,504
Stay of prosecution?

433
00:29:16,505 --> 00:29:18,105
He thinks you lied...

434
00:29:18,106 --> 00:29:19,706
to cover for your client.

435
00:29:20,305 --> 00:29:22,445
- I didn't lie. - Exactly.

436
00:29:22,446 --> 00:29:24,274
He's confused because you confessed...

437
00:29:24,275 --> 00:29:25,975
when he had no proof of it.

438
00:29:26,545 --> 00:29:29,015
Letting just the two get indicted for what I planned...

439
00:29:30,515 --> 00:29:32,014
Without helping Lee escape,

440
00:29:32,015 --> 00:29:34,686
your other clients have a mountain of other charges.

441
00:29:35,255 --> 00:29:37,095
This trial isn't an easy one.

442
00:29:37,096 --> 00:29:38,824
Lee has a flashy past,

443
00:29:38,825 --> 00:29:40,265
and the media will chew her out.

444
00:29:40,366 --> 00:29:42,824
Do you think Da Jung and Su Ho will be any different?

445
00:29:42,825 --> 00:29:43,995
They have records.

446
00:29:44,295 --> 00:29:47,705
The wisest thing to do is to defend them in court.

447
00:29:47,706 --> 00:29:49,336
Not go down with them.

448
00:29:49,505 --> 00:29:51,936
To do that, you have to scale a mountain already,

449
00:29:52,735 --> 00:29:54,606
without adding to the height.

