818
00:51:36,616 --> 00:51:39,726
They let model prisoners take it for social adjustment.

819
00:51:39,826 --> 00:51:41,257
Were you a model prisoner?

820
00:51:41,427 --> 00:51:42,627
I said I'd try it.

821
00:51:43,527 --> 00:51:44,727
I'll pay you the lawyer's fee.

822
00:51:45,427 --> 00:51:47,967
I don't think that has anything to do with this.

823
00:51:50,936 --> 00:51:53,666
I'm proud of you. A model prisoner.

824
00:51:55,607 --> 00:51:56,607
Whatever.

825
00:52:04,516 --> 00:52:07,386
(Chungwoon Prison)

826
00:52:27,036 --> 00:52:28,076
