837
00:53:18,826 --> 00:53:20,427
Slow down.

838
00:53:24,096 --> 00:53:26,527
Go straight, Ro Um.

839
00:53:28,697 --> 00:53:29,797
I think I did it.

840
00:53:30,197 --> 00:53:33,436
Now, let's take it slowly from the top.

841
00:53:33,967 --> 00:53:35,435
Which way is the left turn?

842
00:53:35,436 --> 00:53:38,547
Left turn. Left hand. Left side.

843
00:53:38,947 --> 00:53:40,006
Left.

844
00:53:40,007 --> 00:53:41,777
Try it with the steering wheel.

845
00:53:41,877 --> 00:53:44,615
Left turn. Left side.

846
00:53:44,616 --> 00:53:45,686
Right turn.

847
00:53:46,416 --> 00:53:48,555
Right. Right hand.

848
00:53:48,556 --> 00:53:50,987
No, right side. Right turn.

849
00:53:51,286 --> 00:53:53,157
You're too slow.

850
00:53:53,757 --> 00:53:56,726
Why would you turn left and turn right right after?

851
00:53:56,897 --> 00:53:58,726
I'm not saying that it's the actual route.

852
00:54:00,127 --> 00:54:01,837
You'll be in a car accident, at this rate.

853
00:54:02,697 --> 00:54:04,366
Then, you can defend me.

854
00:54:05,436 --> 00:54:08,076
Don't ever say that with a straight face.

855
00:54:09,636 --> 00:54:10,906
Then, let me try again.

856
00:54:10,907 --> 00:54:12,146
- No. - I can do it.

857
00:54:12,147 --> 00:54:13,345
- No, Ro Um. - I'll do it well.

858
00:54:13,346 --> 00:54:15,615
- Let's take a short break. - Left turn.

859
00:54:15,616 --> 00:54:16,646
