860
00:54:16,647 --> 00:54:19,317
Your probation officer is...

861
00:54:20,346 --> 00:54:21,416
Ms. Lee Ro Um.

862
00:54:24,186 --> 00:54:25,186
Hi.

863
00:54:32,226 --> 00:54:33,527
Lee Ro Um.

864
00:54:49,246 --> 00:54:50,416
We're in love.

865
00:54:52,147 --> 00:54:55,016
I thought you'd have nothing to do. But you've been pretty busy.

866
00:54:57,186 --> 00:54:58,356
The task force to retrieve...

867
00:54:58,357 --> 00:54:59,526
the criminal proceeds of Navis Well-being...

868
00:54:59,527 --> 00:55:02,127
is expanding the scope of redemption.

869
00:55:02,357 --> 00:55:04,725
By inviting experts in the legal, digital,

870
00:55:04,726 --> 00:55:08,067
and financial field to complement the judiciary procedure...

871
00:55:09,666 --> 00:55:11,306
- Me? - Yes.

872
00:55:12,136 --> 00:55:13,967
I'd like you to help us.

873
00:55:14,737 --> 00:55:16,205
The Cyber Bureau...

874
00:55:16,206 --> 00:55:18,777
and Asset Recovery Team are recruiting too,

875
00:55:18,976 --> 00:55:20,575
but no one knows...

876
00:55:20,576 --> 00:55:22,817
the Jeokmok mechanism as well as you.

877
00:55:23,217 --> 00:55:25,217
You'll be an unofficial team member.

878
00:55:25,587 --> 00:55:27,016
Your identity will be protected.

879
00:55:27,447 --> 00:55:29,257
You'll be a specialized member.

880
00:55:31,987 --> 00:55:34,056
The one who knows best about a con...

881
00:55:35,596 --> 00:55:36,757
is a con artist.

882
00:55:48,737 --> 00:55:49,976
Do it if you want to.

883
00:55:51,947 --> 00:55:53,107
What do you think?

884
00:55:53,877 --> 00:55:55,016
You sound interested.

885
00:55:56,317 --> 00:55:58,786
I never told you why I joined Jeokmok, right?

886
00:56:07,257 --> 00:56:09,757
It was the first place that acknowledged me.

887
00:56:10,857 --> 00:56:12,366
So Dam was sick,

888
00:56:12,897 --> 00:56:14,836
and my parents were busy working.

889
00:56:14,837 --> 00:56:17,197
I was alone at school and at home,

890
00:56:17,636 --> 00:56:19,407
and they were the first to praise me.

891
00:56:22,377 --> 00:56:24,136
It's a simple and stupid reason.

892
00:56:25,107 --> 00:56:26,706
I wondered a lot...

893
00:56:27,677 --> 00:56:30,516
if it would've been different if any other group had picked me.

894
00:56:31,616 --> 00:56:33,246
Just do it. Why wonder?

895
00:56:34,857 --> 00:56:35,857
It feels like...

896
00:56:36,616 --> 00:56:39,627
I'm the only one clinging to the past.

897
00:56:40,286 --> 00:56:41,496
It's a sense of duty.

898
00:56:42,297 --> 00:56:44,297
If you're competent and have a sense of duty,

899
00:56:45,726 --> 00:56:46,967
do good for society.

900
00:56:47,366 --> 00:56:48,596
And be acknowledged.

901
00:56:49,636 --> 00:56:51,337
- What about you? - What about me?

902
00:56:51,737 --> 00:56:53,766
I think he's considering you too.

903
00:56:57,636 --> 00:56:59,246
I'll live a boring life.

904
00:56:59,877 --> 00:57:01,047
I can't be bothered.

905
00:57:33,547 --> 00:57:35,177
I'd always wanted to ask.

906
00:57:36,677 --> 00:57:38,047
What makes you laugh?

907
00:57:38,286 --> 00:57:39,717
Bring Ro Um.

908
00:57:40,846 --> 00:57:43,185
She won't visit as long as you live.

909
00:57:43,186 --> 00:57:45,927
I'll be out in a few years.

910
00:57:46,786 --> 00:57:48,357
That won't happen either.

911
00:57:49,127 --> 00:57:50,697
Appeal all you want.

912
00:57:51,826 --> 00:57:54,837
We can't do anything about the charges that expired,

913
00:57:55,136 --> 00:57:57,467
but you'll stand trial until you're sick of it.

914
00:57:57,866 --> 00:58:00,166
In your dreams, even in death.

915
00:58:00,837 --> 00:58:02,107
You came here to say that?

916
00:58:02,607 --> 00:58:03,677
And one more thing.

917
00:58:04,547 --> 00:58:09,047
Don't do anything, however callous or crass...

918
00:58:09,416 --> 00:58:10,746
to get to us.

919
00:58:11,317 --> 00:58:12,317
What if I do?

920
00:58:12,587 --> 00:58:14,087
Unlike Ro Um,

921
00:58:14,416 --> 00:58:16,657
I don't care if you live or die.

922
00:58:18,786 --> 00:58:21,357
It wasn't a mistake that I let you live.

923
00:58:36,036 --> 00:58:37,076
I'm sorry.

924
00:58:39,877 --> 00:58:42,746
I never thought that like me,

925
00:58:44,647 --> 00:58:45,786
you were a living person.

926
00:58:47,987 --> 00:58:49,157
So back then,

927
00:58:50,717 --> 00:58:52,157
I felt no guilt.

928
00:58:54,286 --> 00:58:56,056
If the statues hadn't expired,

929
00:58:56,797 --> 00:58:59,496
I'd be in prison for conning you.

930
00:59:01,366 --> 00:59:03,096
You're not bad at all.

931
00:59:05,036 --> 00:59:07,036
The scumbags are the ones who made you do it.

932
00:59:15,547 --> 00:59:16,547
I apologize.

933
00:59:19,547 --> 00:59:22,516
I dreamed of it every night for ten years.

934
00:59:25,226 --> 00:59:26,286
Of that night.

935
00:59:29,357 --> 00:59:31,967
So I know how horrible it is.

936
00:59:36,837 --> 00:59:37,866
I wanted to...

937
00:59:39,737 --> 00:59:42,177
tell you to sleep soundly.

938
00:59:45,806 --> 00:59:46,877
Because now,

939
00:59:48,777 --> 00:59:50,147
I can sleep peacefully.

940
00:59:51,317 --> 00:59:53,147
Thanks to Moo Young.

941
01:00:06,166 --> 01:00:07,166
Next up.

942
01:00:07,467 --> 01:00:09,095
The Navisgate mastermind,

943
01:00:09,096 --> 01:00:11,135
Lee Jay was arrested a year ago.

944
01:00:11,136 --> 01:00:13,736
From Jeokmok Foundation to Navis Well-being,

945
01:00:13,737 --> 01:00:17,135
a total of 42 people were indicted for their involvement,

946
01:00:17,136 --> 01:00:19,377
and nine were sentenced so far.

947
01:00:19,806 --> 01:00:23,346
Lee Jay is still involved in over 30 lawsuits,

948
01:00:23,516 --> 01:00:26,647
and as things drag on, the longer his sentence has become.

949
01:00:41,636 --> 01:00:44,166
(Ramyeon)

950
01:00:46,936 --> 01:00:48,677
You went through a lot.

951
01:00:52,147 --> 01:00:53,377
For having...

952
01:00:55,677 --> 01:00:56,777
a daughter like me.

953
01:01:08,397 --> 01:01:10,427
This is all I have. Do you mind?

954
01:01:20,936 --> 01:01:21,936
Zero sugar?

955
01:01:23,036 --> 01:01:24,076
It's not bad.

956
01:01:25,206 --> 01:01:26,206
Here.

957
01:01:28,147 --> 01:01:30,777
Check the amendments and sign it.

958
01:01:36,686 --> 01:01:37,986
