959
01:01:37,987 --> 01:01:40,386
(Lee Ro Um, Han Moo Young)

960
01:01:42,357 --> 01:01:43,656
(Lee Ro Um, Han Moo Young)

961
01:01:43,657 --> 01:01:48,237
(Lee Ro Um)

962
01:01:48,737 --> 01:01:49,737
And here.

963
01:01:54,636 --> 01:01:56,306
Once the money's wired,

964
01:01:57,206 --> 01:01:58,246
is it over?

965
01:01:59,407 --> 01:02:01,246
It's over between you and me.

966
01:02:08,456 --> 01:02:09,487
The contract, I mean.

967
01:02:12,987 --> 01:02:15,096
I don't want to have to defend you now.

968
01:02:22,366 --> 01:02:24,805
Su Ho, where are the zip ties?

969
01:02:24,806 --> 01:02:26,467
Oh, I have them.

970
01:02:27,706 --> 01:02:28,806
Hey, Ro Um.

971
01:02:29,107 --> 01:02:30,975
I think you were conned.

972
01:02:30,976 --> 01:02:32,475
The lights here are nice,

973
01:02:32,476 --> 01:02:33,745
but did you go upstairs?

974
01:02:33,746 --> 01:02:34,946
The bathroom tiles are cracked...

975
01:02:34,947 --> 01:02:36,546
and the door doesn't shut.

976
01:02:36,547 --> 01:02:37,616
Work, don't talk.

977
01:02:39,186 --> 01:02:41,416
Get the landlord to fix that.

978
01:02:41,717 --> 01:02:43,286
Can't you fix it now?

979
01:02:43,657 --> 01:02:45,587
I will, okay?

980
01:02:45,987 --> 01:02:47,685
But have them pay for it.

981
01:02:47,686 --> 01:02:49,197
Don't let it slide.

982
01:02:50,496 --> 01:02:51,766
Will Moo Young come too?

983
01:02:52,096 --> 01:02:53,096
No.

984
01:02:54,766 --> 01:02:56,467
You didn't tell him we moved?

985
01:02:57,436 --> 01:02:59,636
No. Should I?

