01:03:44,987 --> 01:03:46,587
Play or lose, rock-paper-scissors.

993
01:03:47,016 --> 01:03:48,785
- Rock-paper-scissors. - Rock-paper-scissors.

994
01:03:48,786 --> 01:03:50,556
- Okay. - Darn!

995
01:03:51,826 --> 01:03:53,956
Be honest. Did you plan this?

996
01:03:55,496 --> 01:03:57,055
Lee Ro Um, was it you?

997
01:03:57,056 --> 01:03:58,056
Look into my...

998
01:03:59,527 --> 01:04:00,726
I can't tell.

999
01:04:01,967 --> 01:04:02,967
Why me?

1000
01:04:03,397 --> 01:04:05,865
Why the heck is it always me?

1001
01:04:05,866 --> 01:04:08,836
This doesn't make any sense.

1002
01:04:08,837 --> 01:04:11,606
Unless you planned this, there's no way I'm always the one.

1003
01:04:11,607 --> 01:04:15,146
Hey, if you think about it, I'm the eldest here, okay?

1004
01:04:15,147 --> 01:04:16,575
Remember that.

1005
01:04:16,576 --> 01:04:18,516
I'm doing this for you, you know.

1006
01:04:19,246 --> 01:04:21,785
That's not easy for a guy like me.

1007
01:04:21,786 --> 01:04:22,786
Hello?

1008
01:04:23,286 --> 01:04:24,587
Ro Um, it's me.

1009
01:04:26,157 --> 01:04:27,857
I see you paid me.

1010
01:04:28,596 --> 01:04:30,157
I'm glad you got it.

1011
01:04:30,456 --> 01:04:32,797
You forgot a few zeros.

1012
01:04:33,496 --> 01:04:34,496
Who did?

1013
01:04:35,036 --> 01:04:36,237
You did.

1014
01:04:36,797 --> 01:04:39,107
- That can't be. - Can you check for me?

1015
01:04:39,567 --> 01:04:40,706
Fine.

1016
01:04:41,206 --> 01:04:42,976
Can you do it right now?

1017
01:04:44,337 --> 01:04:46,047
- When I'm free. - Are you busy?

1018
01:04:46,806 --> 01:04:48,947
- What are you doing? - I'm moving.

1019
01:04:49,476 --> 01:04:51,786
You're moving. Congratulations.

1020
01:04:52,047 --> 01:04:54,416
