1021
01:04:54,746 --> 01:04:55,757
I have.

1022
01:05:05,567 --> 01:05:06,567
Gosh.

1023
01:05:08,067 --> 01:05:09,096
Nice house.

1024
01:05:10,636 --> 01:05:12,136
How did you know the address?

1025
01:05:13,306 --> 01:05:16,076
Well, there's someone who shares me such stuff.

1026
01:05:24,377 --> 01:05:27,487
So? You came all the way for money?

1027
01:05:27,817 --> 01:05:28,886
No.

1028
01:05:32,357 --> 01:05:33,627
I have something to tell you.

